OL,3,CCar crashes on 20mph and 30mph roads
OL,4,Cdrop by almost a quarter in spring
OL,6,FThe number of car crashes on 20mph and
OL,7,F30mph roads fell by almost a quarter
OL,8,Fthis spring, new figures show.
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government said the latest
OL,11,Fpolice-recorded road collision
OL,12,Fstatistics from April to June 2024
OL,13,Fshow that both collisions (24%) and
OL,14,Fcasualties (24%) on 20mph and 30mph
OL,15,Froads (combined) fell by almost a
OL,16,Fquarter compared to the same period in
OL,17,F2023.
