OL,3,CCar crashes on 20mph and 30mph roads
OL,4,Cdrop by almost a quarter in spring
OL,6,FIt comes after the introduction of the
OL,7,Fdefault 20mph speed limit in built-up
OL,8,Fareas in Wales in September 2023,
OL,9,Fwhich proved controversial.
OL,11,FWelsh Government said that in the
OL,12,Ffirst nine months since the
OL,13,Fintroduction of the policy, the number
OL,14,Fof collisions (26%) and casualties
OL,15,F(28%) on 20mph and 30mph roads
OL,16,F(combined) were down by more than a
OL,17,Fquarter, saying the three quarterly
OL,18,Freductions within this period were the
OL,19,Fthree largest quarterly reductions
OL,20,Foutside the Covid pandemic.
