OL,3,CCar crashes on 20mph and 30mph roads
OL,4,Cdrop by almost a quarter in spring
OL,6,FIt said the data is impacted by
OL,7,Fseasonal factors such as traffic
OL,8,Fvolume and weather conditions.
OL,10,FWales' transport secretary Ken Skates
OL,11,FMS said: "The data published today
OL,12,Fprovides encouraging signs that things
OL,13,Fare moving in the right direction,
OL,14,Fwith a fall year-on-year in collisions
OL,15,Fand casualties - the lowest on record
OL,16,Foutside the Covid pandemic period.
