OL,3,CCar crashes on 20mph and 30mph roads
OL,4,Cdrop by almost a quarter in spring
OL,6,F"We recognise there is still a way to
OL,7,Fgo, we've always said it will take
OL,8,Fmany years before we see any
OL,9,Fsignificant impact, but these figures
OL,10,Fare beginning to show a positive trend
OL,11,Ftowards making our roads safer for
OL,12,Feveryone.
OL,14,F"Local Authorities are currently
OL,15,Freviewing the feedback from their
OL,16,Fcitizens and assessing it against our
OL,17,Frevised guidance to make sure they
OL,18,Fhave the right speeds on the right
OL,19,Froads, with road safety being at the
OL,20,Fheart of any decision made."
